snippet mwvimplug "mediawiki - vim plugin" w
{| class=wikitable width=100%
|-
|width=72pt|${1:[http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=${2:9999} vim.org]}
|width=72pt|[${3:https://github.com/owner/plugin} GitHub]
!width=15%|${4:plugin}
|${5:Plugin one-line description}
|-
|colspan=4|
{|
|-
|{{kb|$0}} || Shortcut
|}
|}
Plugin high-level description, or comment on the configuration.
<source lang="vim">
Plug '...'                " Plugin installation
</source>
<source lang="vim">
" Plugin configuration
</source>
endsnippet

